OL,3,COver half of election candidates faced
OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FThe government's advisor on political
OL,7,Fviolence told ITV News of the risk of
OL,8,F"violent attacks which have seen
OL,9,Ffrontline politicians be murdered", as
OL,10,FITV News Political Correspondent
OL,11,FShehab Khan reports
OL,13,FWords by Political Correspondent
OL,14,FShehab Khan and Politics Producer Maya
OL,15,FBowles
OL,17,FMore than half the candidates in the
OL,18,FJuly General Election faced
OL,19,Fharassment, intimidation, or abuse,
OL,20,Faccording to a major report by the
OL,21,Felections watchdog.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
