OL,3,COver half of election candidates faced
OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FThe findings from the Electoral
OL,7,FCommission reveal a concerning level
OL,8,Fof hostility directed at those running
OL,9,Ffor office.
OL,11,FReacting to the report, the
OL,12,Fgovernment's advisor on political
OL,13,Fviolence, Lord Walney, told ITV News
OL,14,Fthat without more government action to
OL,15,Ftackle threats against candidates and
OL,16,FMPs, "we risk repeats of the kind of
OL,17,Fviolent attacks which have seen
OL,18,Ffrontline politicians be murdered".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
