OL,3,COver half of election candidates faced
OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FThe review revealed 55% of candidates
OL,7,Fencountered some form of abuse or
OL,8,Fintimidation, while 56% opted to avoid
OL,9,Fcertain campaign activities out of
OL,10,Ffear for their safety.
OL,12,FChief Executive of the Electoral
OL,13,FCommission Vijay Rangarajan said the
OL,14,Flevel of harassment and intimidation
OL,15,Ffaced by candidates was "concerning"
OL,16,Fand requires "urgent and coordinated
OL,17,Faction."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
