OL,6,FHe warned the abuse is "deterring some
OL,7,Fpeople from standing to be candidates,
OL,8,Fand inhibiting how some engage with
OL,9,Fvoters".
OL,11,FPreet Gill, the Labour MP for
OL,12,FBirmingham Edgbaston, said she's no
OL,13,Fstranger to abuse, but that this
OL,14,Felection was unprecedented in terms of
OL,15,Fthe harassment she faced.
