OL,6,FDuring the campaign she had to report
OL,7,Fincidents to the police four times,
OL,8,Fafter she was verbally harassed while
OL,9,Fout with her daughter, had her
OL,10,Fcampaign placards targeted by vandals,
OL,11,Fand received abuse and death threats
OL,12,Fon social media.
OL,14,F"It's not fair game that MPs should
OL,15,Fput up with this... I want to be able
OL,16,Fto walk about freely like everybody
OL,17,Felse", she told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
