OL,6,FShe revealed her teenage children have
OL,7,Fbecome aware of the kind of daily
OL,8,Fthreats she faces, adding: "They
OL,9,Flegitimately ask me, 'Is someone going
OL,10,Fto kill you?'"
OL,12,F"When my daughter said that to me, I
OL,13,Fjust burst into tears."
OL,15,FMany of the threats Gill faced during
OL,16,Fthis election were from people unhappy
OL,17,Fwith Labour's response to the war in
OL,18,FGaza. The words "murderer" and "blood
OL,19,Fon hands" were written on her campaign
OL,20,Fposters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
