OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FDiscussions about the safety of MPs'
OL,7,Fhave escalated since the October 7
OL,8,FHamas attacks in 2023 and the Israeli
OL,9,Fmilitary campaign in Gaza - with
OL,10,Fheightened tensions about the conflict
OL,11,Fspilling into the campaign trail for
OL,12,Fmany candidates in the July election.
OL,14,FThe Electoral Commission report
OL,15,Fhighlighted: "Ongoing international
OL,16,Ftensions in some cases led to an
OL,17,Fincrease in antisemitic and
OL,18,FIslamophobic abuse directed at
OL,19,Fcandidates."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
