OL,3,COver half of election candidates faced
OL,4,Cabuse and harassment: report
OL,6,FThe murders of MPs Jo Cox in 2016 and
OL,7,FSir David Amess in 2021 shook
OL,8,FWestminster, sparking a whole new
OL,9,Fdebate about the safety of our elected
OL,10,Frepresentatives.
OL,12,FWhile the government has increased
OL,13,Fsecurity funding and support for MPs,
OL,14,Ftheir own advisor on political
OL,15,Fviolence urged them to go further.
OL,17,FLord Walney told ITV News:
OL,18,F"Unfortunately we risk repeats of the
OL,19,Fkind of violent attacks which have
OL,20,Fseen front line politicians be
OL,21,Fmurdered"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
