OL,6,FThis is an issue that defies party
OL,7,Flines.
OL,9,FNigel Farage, the leader of Reform UK,
OL,10,Fhad a milkshake thrown at him during
OL,11,Fthe election campaign. And one of his
OL,12,Fparty's candidates, Steve Rubidge,
OL,13,Fsuffered "severely torn ligaments"
OL,14,Fafter an altercation while out
OL,15,Fcampaigning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
