OL,6,FRubidge was handing out leaflets in
OL,7,Fthe Truro and Falmouth constituency
OL,8,Fwhen a man started verbally harassing
OL,9,Fhim and then stole his bag with
OL,10,Fcampaign materials, wallet and keys
OL,11,Finside.
OL,13,FMr Rubidge said he chased the man, and
OL,14,Fa physical tussle ensued as he tried
OL,15,Fto grab the bag back. He alleges the
OL,16,Fman punched and hit him.
OL,18,F"It did make me think - is this worth
OL,19,Fit?" he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
