OL,6,F"It was right at the beginning of my
OL,7,Fcampaign... you're then more wary
OL,8,Fabout how people are reacting,
OL,9,Fespecially the ones that start
OL,10,Fshouting at you in the street."
OL,12,FParliament welcomed a major new step
OL,13,Fin efforts to tackle the threats MPs
OL,14,Fface in October, as it agreed to set
OL,15,Fup a Speaker's Conference to look at
OL,16,Fthe issue.
OL,18,FThere have only been eight Speaker's
OL,19,FConferences in the last hundred years,
OL,20,Fusually convened to tackle issues
OL,21,Faround elections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
