OL,6,FIt will consider factors influencing
OL,7,Fthe threat levels against candidates
OL,8,Fand MPs during the election period and
OL,9,Fthe effectiveness of the response to
OL,10,Fthose threats.
OL,12,FA House of Commons spokesperson told
OL,13,FITV News that abuse and intimidation
OL,14,Fwas "completely unacceptable" and that
OL,15,Fit is "fundamental to our democracy"
OL,16,Fthat MPs and their staff are able to
OL,17,Fdo their jobs safely.
